OL,3,CMan died due to ambulance crew's
OL,4,C'gross failure in basic care'
OL,6,FThe Coroner adds that the advanced
OL,7,Flife support given to Mr Irvine by the
OL,8,Fcrew after his cardiac arrest was
OL,9,F"inadequate in a number of respects"
OL,10,Fand could have contributed to his
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,FThe two medics involved, ambulance
OL,14,Ftechnician Tom Le Sauteur and
OL,15,Fparamedic John Sutherland, were found
OL,16,Fguilty of failing to provide adequate
OL,17,Fcare to Mr Irvine under Jersey's
OL,18,FHealth and Safety Law last June.
