OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1749840343
OL,3,CMan died due to ambulance crew's
OL,4,C'gross failure in basic care'
OL,6,FThey were sentenced to a two-year
OL,7,Fconditional discharge and ordered to
OL,8,Fpay #500 each in court costs - both
OL,9,Fmen ultimately resigned from the
OL,10,FAmbulance Service at the start of this
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThe Coroner states that on Friday 18
OL,14,FMarch 2022, Mr Irvine was "very drunk
OL,15,Fand had taken some prescription drugs
OL,16,Fwhen he called an ambulance asking for
OL,17,Fassistance".
OL,19,FShe says he met the two medics "with
OL,20,Fambivalence and at times, verbal
OL,21,Faggression".
