OL,3,CMan died due to ambulance crew's
OL,4,C'gross failure in basic care'
OL,6,FMr Irvine then fell to the floor on
OL,7,Fthe landing outside his flat but
OL,8,Fconcerned that they could face further
OL,9,Faggression, the Coroner explains the
OL,10,Fmedics "conducted no physical
OL,11,Fobservations of Frazer before police
OL,12,Farrived".
OL,14,FHowever, she adds: "Frazer's level of
OL,15,Fconsciousness was deteriorating and
OL,16,Fthere were clear signs that this was
OL,17,Fhappening.
