PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1749840343
OL,3,CMan died due to ambulance crew's
OL,4,C'gross failure in basic care'
OL,6,F"After the police crew arrived, there
OL,7,Fwas no good reason that steps could
OL,8,Fnot then have been taken to conduct
OL,9,Fobservations ... Yet for at least 12
OL,10,Fminutes he was still not placed in a
OL,11,Frecovery position and nothing was done
OL,12,Fby the ambulance crew to effectively
OL,13,Fassess and manage his airway."
OL,15,FThe Coroner concludes: "There was an
OL,16,Funreasonable and protracted delay by
OL,17,Fthe ambulance in providing basic care
OL,18,Fto him.
