OL,3,CMan died due to ambulance crew's
OL,4,C'gross failure in basic care'
OL,6,F"They say your legacy is what you
OL,7,Fleave in people. Frazer will never see
OL,8,Fhis dreams come to fruition.
OL,10,F"He was too big a personality to ever
OL,11,Fbe forgotten. His passing has
OL,12,Fdevastated our family, and he is
OL,13,Fmissed every day."
